## Input

```css
@media (#{$feature}) {
  .box {
    color: red;
  }
}

@media (#{$feature}: #{$value}) {
  .box {
    color: red;
  }
}

@media (#{$min} <= width <= #{$max}) {
  .box {
    color: red;
  }
}

@media (#{$min} <= width) {
  .box {
    color: red;
  }
}

@media (min-width: #{$value}px) {
  .box {
    color: red;
  }
}

@media (#{$min}px <= width) {
  .box {
    color: red;
  }
}

@container (#{$feature}: #{$value}) {
  .box {
    color: red;
  }
}

@container (min-width: #{$value}px) {
  .box {
    color: red;
  }
}

```


